To use the Datadog Agent Integrations, you need to enable them in the
Datadog Agent configuration.

Each integration has its own configuration file in:
%%ETCDIR%%/conf.d/<integration>.d/conf.yaml

Example configuration files are provided as:
%%ETCDIR%%/conf.d/<integration>.d/conf.yaml.example

For more information, see:
https://docs.datadoghq.com/integrations/
